WHAT IS IT?
-----------

  'Pivoto', a Workbench game, is played on a 7 by 7 tiles board;
your goal is to remove all the 'front facing' (facing toward you)
coloured tiles by aligning them with adjacent tiles (either
horizontally or vertically) of the same colour. The more tiles of
the same colour that are next to each other, the more points you
make.

  Avoid isolating tiles, I.E.: front facing tiles that have one
colour, but none of the neighbouring tiles have a face of the
same colour.

  Have fun!

